data.description: Here is your opportunity to live in the beautiful community of Venice Gardens!! Conveniently located close to shopping and dining this quaint neighborhood is the ideal place to call home. Public water and sewer is a great benefit to living here. There is an optional HOA of $150 a year to use the community pool and rec center down by the public park. This home has 2 completely renovated bathrooms. Master has a large walk in shower. A large circular drive allows for plenty of parking along with the RV parking on the side of the home. New Roof, new electrical panel, new baths, new kitchen cabinets plus appliances. The home has new ceiling fans in every bedroom.
